title: The Doors - Television Skies (3-CD) 2008 - 2018 ak256
description:
The Doors - Television Skies: 33 tracks on 3 Discs 2008-2018ak256 

From the original post shared by buckybarnes...
So I was cleaning out some boxes a few weeks ago and came across an old box of CDs I’d long since converted to WAV files on my hard drives. I had the old ‘Complete Matrix Tapes’, 'The Doors: Complete' [an anthology style collection but not in chronological order], and a few other single disc early 90’s ‘bootlegs.’ As I was looking at them, I said to myself, “Shit, I could make sets as good, if not better!” – I also went through youtube and put together a playlist of all the Doors TV appearances to go with the artwork! I hope everyone enjoys it...
And so do I so again thankx to buckybarnes for this collection
